args:
With the empire's assault becoming fiercer,
Lily and Victor set Operation 'Chuting Stars—
their final plan—into action, putting everything
on the line to protect Dragonyule.
They're dressed like Saint Starfall!\nYou don't think they're...
We won't let you mock us ever again!
It's the Dragonyule defenders from hell—\nthe scary dude and cute kid everyone's\ntalking about!
Is THAT what they're calling us now?
Let them say what they want. More\nimportantly, we've confirmed that this\ntown was their next target after all.
What of it? We had plenty of time to get\nready for you, too! You're not stopping us!
We'll chop you down to size!
But we're stronger! With me, men!
We're getting roasted like freakin'\nchestnuts out here. These guys are FIERCE!
And we're just getting started.\nNow, Victor!
I dunno, but it makes for quite a sight!
Ahhh... A white Dragonyule.\nHow romantic. To glimpse such\ncrystalline purity, falling from on high—
There's more snow where that came from!
Argh! I can't see a thing!\nHow're we supposed to retreat now?
Right. Nobody ruins Dragonyule on my\nwatch!
What's with all the noise outside?
Whoa! Presents're falling from the sky!
Oh! Keep the window closed tonight,\nall right, sweetheart? Now go to sleep.
Are...my eyes playing tricks on me?
I think you're right. And not just one—\ntwo kind yet strong Saint Starfalls are\ngoing to save this town tonight.
